n-first-thought-095017928.html">任天堂认为今年 Switch 游戏机的销量将超过预期</a></h2><h3>而且 Switch 已经很旧了。</h3> <a href="https://www.engadget.com/nintendo-believes-itll-sell-more-switch-consoles-than-first-thought-095017928.html"><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2024-02/7d4fa710-c5a2-11ee-affd-5c9b1c63806c" data-crop-orig-src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2024-02/7d4fa710-c5a2-11ee-affd-5c9b1c63806c" style="height:450px;width:675px;" alt="TMA" data-uuid="f401a083-c9f2-3423-8bda-64fafb0ec0ca"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">恩杰特</div></figure></a><p>任天堂 Switch 已经问世近七年了，它证明了这款混合游戏机仍然有生命力。任天堂的寿命足以提高其本财年的预测销售数据。在第三季度财报中，该公司宣布将 Switch 的预计销量从 1500 万台增加到 1550 万台。这很好，但是<a data-i13n="cpos:12;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/nintendo-is-said-to-be-showing-the-switch-2s-dlss-and-ray-tracing-capabilities-to-developers-161050817.html">Switch 2</a>在哪里？</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:13;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/nintendo-believes-itll-sell-more-switch-consoles-than-first-thought-095017928.html"><strong>继续阅读。</strong></a></p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/the-morning-after-twitter-alternative-bluesky-is-no-longer-invitation-only-121534911.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/the-morning-after-twitter-alternative-bluesky-is-no-longer-invitation-only-121534911.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> e3b6a420-7c4b-42f9-a1d6-6c2844c598c3 </guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Mat Smith]]></dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Wed, 07 Feb 2024 12:15:34 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1707301506</ingested><modified> 2024-02-07T10:25:23+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Media]]></category><category><![CDATA[Celebrities]]></category><category><![CDATA[Arts & Entertainment]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[