et]]></dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Tue, 06 Feb 2024 22:50:50 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1707312003</ingested><modified> 2024-02-07T13:20:07+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Sports & Recreation]]></category><category><![CDATA[Professional Services]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Pranav Dixit]]></category><media:content height="932" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2024-01%2F17620530-c541-11ee-b5fe-c4ea0fa98930&amp;resize=1400%2C932&amp;client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&amp;signature=060b10c66888f80aa7b89759cb21268fbc74a801" width="1400"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="932" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2024-01%2Ff3f4ce70-c540-11ee-a77f-2617f627f597&amp;resize=1400%2C932&amp;client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&amp;signature=39f9c5ce812a8691cf53ede040c5bf44de25b843" width="1400"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ASSOCIATED PRESS]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[AFC tight end David Njoku (85), of the Cleveland Browns, runs after catching a pass as NFC defensive back Darius Slay (2) defends during the flag football event at the NFL Pro Bowl football game on Sunday, Feb. 4, 2024 in Orlando, Fla. (Phelan M. Ebenhack/AP Images for the NFL)]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Pro Bowl Football]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Former Mandalorian actor Gina Carano sues Disney — with X’s help]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p> <a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2018-12-12-star-wars-disney-plus-the-mandalorian-cast.html">前搭档卡尔·韦瑟斯</a>去世四天后，曾出演<em>《曼达洛人》的</em>演员吉娜·卡拉诺在埃隆·马斯克的帮助下起诉迪士尼和卢卡斯影业，要求其退出该剧。卡拉诺的后迪士尼作品包括一部由阴谋理论家本·夏皮罗制作的电影，他周二在 X 上<a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:2;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://twitter.com/ginacarano/status/1754952279646437655" data-original-link="https://twitter.com/ginacarano/status/1754952279646437655">发帖称</a>，“事实是，我在我喜欢的每一篇帖子上发布的所有内容都遭到追捕，因为我不符合可接受的叙述的时间。” X 在给 Engadget 的一份声明中确认了其提供的协助。</p><p>卡拉诺在 X 上发表了一篇 694 字的帖子， <a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:3;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://twitter.com/ginacarano/status/1754952279646437655" data-original-link="https://twitter.com/ginacarano/status/1754952279646437655">分享了</a>这起诉讼的消息。在这篇文章中，她声称从未使用过攻击性语言，将共和党人与大屠杀期间的犹太人进行比较，也没有写过任何种族主义或跨性别者恐惧症的内容。她坚称，她的男搭档“被允许在不受骚扰、再教育课程或解雇的情况下发言”，但她“没有被赋予行使言论自由的同等权利”。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p> “当我们开始工作时，艺术家不会放弃我们作为美国公民的权利，”卡拉诺周二写道。然而，由于她没有因为自己的观点而被捕或拘留，她作为美国公民的权利似乎完全不受侵犯。与此同时，迪士尼等美国企业有权不雇用观点与其品牌冲突的演员。</p><p>这位演员兼前综合格斗选手周二感谢马斯克和X通过帮助资助她的诉讼“给了我揭露我的案子的机会”。马斯克此前曾<a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:4;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://www.npr.org/2023/08/06/1192394226/musk-vows-to-pay-legal-costs-for-users-who-get-in-trouble-at-work-for-their-twee" data-original-link="https://www.npr.org/2023/08/06/1192394226/musk-vows-to-pay-legal-costs-for-users-who-get-in-trouble-at-work-for-their-twee">表示，</a>他将为因在平台上发帖而陷入麻烦的用户支付法律费用。</p><p> X 在给 Engadget 的一份声明中确认了其金钱援助。 “作为 X Corp 对言论自由承诺的标志，我们很自豪能为吉娜·卡拉诺 (Gina Carano) 的诉讼提供财务支持，使她能够寻求维护自己在 X 上的言论自由权以及在不受欺凌、骚扰或歧视的情况下工作的能力，公司发言人写道。 </p><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2024-02/c0a25a90-c538-11ee-bbfd-eb68c71c3aaa" data-crop-orig-src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2024-02/c0a25a90-c538-11ee-bbfd-eb68c71c3aaa" style="height:1333px;width:2000px;" alt="吉娜·卡拉诺在《曼达洛人》第二季中饰演卡拉·沙丘" data-uuid="1ac0c1e7-5996-3f92-a45a-63c31a6513e0"><figcaption>卡拉诺在《曼达洛人》第二季中饰演卡拉·沙丘</figcaption><div class="photo-credit">迪士尼+</div></figure><p>卡拉诺与迪士尼的麻烦源于 X（当时为 Twitter）和 Instagram 上的社交媒体帖子。她在<a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:5;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://www.themarysue.com/why-was-gina-carano-fired-from-the-mandalorian-the-gina-carano-controversy-explained/" data-original-link="https://www.themarysue.com/why-was-gina-carano-fired-from-the-mandalorian-the-gina-carano-controversy-explained/">帖子</a>中质疑 COVID-19 疫苗的有效性，将疫苗接种者的死亡归咎于拜登政府，声称杰弗里·爱泼斯坦没有自杀，并添加了“boop/bop/beep”作为她的代词。</p><p>压垮迪士尼的最后一根稻草是，她在 Instagram 上分享了一篇帖子，暗示特朗普时代的美国保守派所受到的待遇与纳粹时代德国针对犹太人的待遇有相似之处。第二天，迪士尼将卡拉诺从<em>《曼达洛人</em>》和<em>《新共和国游骑兵</em>》系列（现已取消）中剔除。</p><p> “吉娜·卡拉诺目前并未受雇于卢卡斯影业，未来也没有计划，”一位发言人当时在一份声明中写道。 “尽管如此，她在社交媒体上发布的基于文化和宗教身份诽谤他人的帖子是令人憎恶且不可接受的。”卡拉诺的经纪公司联合人才经纪公司大约在同一时间解雇了她。</p><p>卡拉诺在《星球大战》之后的职业生涯包括由本·夏皮罗的<em>《每日电讯报》</em>制作的<em>《草原恐怖》</em> 。她还主演了 2022 年的电影<em>《我的儿子亨特》</em> ，该片“虚构地讲述了美国总统乔·拜登之子亨特·拜登的生活方式和丑闻”。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/former-mandalorian-actor-gina-carano-sues-disney--with-xs-help-220039820.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/former-mandalorian-actor-gina-carano-sues-disney--with-xs-help-220039820.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 1acd7583-7d6d-47ee-a2de-c3dcf4f2dc2d</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Will Shanklin]]></dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Tue, 06 Feb 2024 22:00:39 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1707257505</ingested><modified> 2024-02-06T22:11:51+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Arts & Entertainment]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Will Shanklin]]></category><media:content height="839" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2024-02%2F204d98d0-c53c-11ee-ab3b-849915dcf4a6&amp;resize=1400%2C839&amp;client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&amp;signature=bc819e01415549fbfa477835a78ca381fd2faaf3" width="1400"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="839" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2024-02%2F204d98d0-c53c-11ee-ab3b-849915dcf4a6&amp;resize=1400%2C839&amp;client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&amp;signature=33491d8a21afdd2f2748d9b1bff417e26d65776a" width="1400"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Disney+]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Cara Dune (Gina Carano) and Greef Karga (Carl Weathers) in a season 2 promotional still for The Mandalorian.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Carano with the late Carl Weathers in ‘The Mandalorian’ ]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Phony AI Biden robocalls reached up to 25,000 voters, says New Hampshire AG]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>总部位于德克萨斯州的两家公司与一系列<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/elevenlabs-reportedly-banned-the-account-that-deepfaked-bidens-voice-with-its-ai-tools-083355975.html"><ins>使用人工智能模仿乔·拜登总统的</ins></a>机器人电话有关。音频深度伪造被用来敦促新罕布什尔州选民不要参加该州的总统初选。新罕布什尔州总检察长约翰·福尔梅拉 (John Formella) 表示，1 月份有多达 25,000 个接到该州居民的电话。</p><p>福梅拉表示，一项调查已将自动电话的来源与德克萨斯州的 Life Corporation 和 Lingo Telecom 公司联系起来。目前尚未对任何一家公司或 Life Corporation 的所有者沃尔特·蒙克 (Walter Monk) 提出任何指控。调查正在进行中，据信其他实体也参与其中。据说联邦执法官员也在调查此案。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>据<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.cnn.com/2024/02/06/tech/nh-ag-robocall-update"><em><ins>美国有线电视新闻网</ins></em></a>报道，福尔梅拉在新闻发布会上表示：“我们已向生命公司发出了一封停止函，命令该公司立即停止违反新罕布什尔州选举法。”“我们还展开了刑事调查，我们正在采取下一步调查措施，向 Life Corporation、Lingo Telecom 和任何其他个人或实体发送文件保存通知和传票。”</p><p>美国联邦通信委员会还向 Lingo Telecom 发出了停止函。该机构表示 ( <a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://docs.fcc.gov/public/attachments/DOC-400295A1.pdf"><ins>PDF</ins></a> ) 过去曾就机器人电话向两家公司发出过警告。</p><p> Deepfake 是使用人工智能语音克隆公司 ElevenLabs 的工具创建的，该<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/elevenlabs-reportedly-banned-the-account-that-deepfaked-bidens-voice-with-its-ai-tools-083355975.html"><ins>公司禁止了负责的用户</ins></a>。该公司表示，它“致力于防止音频人工智能工具的滥用，并且非常严肃地对待任何滥用事件。”</p><p>与此同时，美国联邦通信委员会正在<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/the-fcc-wants-to-make-robocalls-that-use-ai-generated-voices-illegal-105628839.html"><ins>寻求禁止使用人工智能生成的语音的自动呼叫</ins></a>。根据《电话消费者保护法》，该机构负责制定有关自动电话的规则。委员们将在未来几周内就该问题进行投票。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/phony-ai-biden-robocalls-reached-up-to-25000-voters-says-new-hampshire-ag-205253966.html?src=rss ]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/phony-ai-biden-robocalls-reached-up-to-25000-voters-says-new-hampshire-ag-205253966.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 76ea6e0d-71fd-4298-a275-29bb592ef74d </guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Kris Holt]]></dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Tue, 06 Feb 2024 20:52:53 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1707252775</ingested><modified> 2024-02-06T20:53:04+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Politics & Government]]></category><category><![CDATA[Company Legal & Law Matters]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Kris Holt]]></category><media:content height="933" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2024-01%2Fa0e52d20-c530-11ee-addf-f3b6cc5eec3c&amp;resize=1400%2C933&amp;client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&amp;signature=1df57f749220dbfa9707cc8f7130e598391744b0" width="1400"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="933" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2024-01%2Fa0e52d20-c530-11ee-addf-f3b6cc5eec3c&amp;resize=1400%2C933&amp;client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&amp;signature=77559e2ecf387f8e4365f34a974d1bcb7db1c923" width="1400"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ASSOCIATED PRESS]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[President Joe Biden delivers remarks on the Emergency National Security Supplemental Appropriations Act in the State Dining Room of the White House, Tuesday, Feb. 6, 2024, in Washington. (AP Photo/Evan Vucci)]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Biden]]></media:title></media:content></item></channel></rss>